    "privacy.tableOfContents.contact": "Makipag-ugnayan sa Amin",
    "privacy.intro.p1": "securememo.app (\"we,\" \"us,\" or \"our\") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Notice explains how we handle information in connection with our service, which allows users to create and share encrypted memos that are deleted after successful read confirmation or expiration. All encryption occurs client-side in your browser, and we do not have access to memo plaintext.",
